trans-unit.source: Exposes <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.ControlType.Document"></xref> control types to [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Expõe <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.ControlType.Document"> </xref> controlar os tipos de para [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The DocumentAutomationPeer represents documents and supports the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>.
trans-unit.target: O DocumentAutomationPeer representa documentos e suporta <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>

trans-unit.source: Objects such as a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument> or <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> can contain embedded objects, such as images and hyperlinks.
trans-unit.target: Objetos, tais como um <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument>ou <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>pode conter objetos incorporados, tais como imagens e hiperligações.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument>

trans-unit.source: Initially, when you try to get the child elements of the document, <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName> does not return the embedded objects.
trans-unit.target: Inicialmente, ao tentar obter o subordinado elementos do documento <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName>não devolve os objetos incorporados.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: To get the embedded elements, obtain a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> from the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern> and call <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Para obter os elementos incorporados, obter um <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange>do <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>e chame <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange>

trans-unit.source: After <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName> is called, any elements in that <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> are returned by <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Depois de <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName>se chama, quaisquer elementos que <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange>são devolvidos pelo <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Unless you know the document is a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>, you should not call <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A> on the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern.DocumentRange%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] >, A menos que sabe o documento é um <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>, não deve chamar <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A>no <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern.DocumentRange%2A?displayProperty=fullName>propriedade.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern.DocumentRange%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>

trans-unit.source: If the document is loaded from a network location, calling <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A> on the entire document is resource intensive.
trans-unit.target: Se o documento é carregado a partir de uma localização de rede, ao chamar <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A>em todo o documento é recurso intensiva.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A>

trans-unit.source: Instead, you should use one of the methods on <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern> that returns a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> that represents a portion of the document.
trans-unit.target: Em vez disso, deve utilizar um dos métodos em <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>que devolve um <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange>que representa uma parte do documento.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>

trans-unit.source: This property does not indicate whether the element is visible.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade indica se o elemento está visível.

trans-unit.source: In some circumstances, an element is on the screen but is still not visible.
trans-unit.target: Em algumas circunstâncias, um elemento está no ecrã, mas é ainda não estão visível.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the element is obscured by other elements, it might not be visible.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, se o elemento é ficar obscurecido por outros elementos, poderá não estar visível.

trans-unit.source: In this case, the method returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: Neste caso, o método devolve `false`.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the element is not on the screen; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
